# ============================================
# NOTE: Schema Updates
# ============================================
# Block schemas are hand-crafted JSON files stored in ./schemas
# When Nexter plugins are updated and block attributes change:
# 1. Manually update or add the affected schema JSON files in ./schemas
# 2. Update index.json, categories.json, and use-cases.json if needed
# 3. Commit: git add schemas/ && git commit -m "Update schemas"
# 4. Push: git push (Dokploy auto-deploys)
